  <p class="left-align">
    <span class="style1">Welcome to Add a Service Wizard</span> <br/>
    
   <br/> The Add a Service Wizard allows you to add a service from a list
     of sample services in the library. This page introduces you to the
     steps involved in this process.

  <br/><br/>
  <strong>What do I do next?</strong><br/>
    When you are ready to continue, press the <b>Next</b> button to continue on to
    the Select Service Type Page. If you would like to exit the Wizard without
    creating a new Service, press the <b>Cancel</b> button.

    <br/><br/>
  <strong>How did I get here?</strong><br/>
    The Add a Service Wizard: Introduction Page appears when you select
    to add a service using a Wizard. The panel on the right gives an overview of each step in the process.
